        | blank area of tab bar will open a new ssh terminal too
      li.pb-1
        code.mr-1 right click
        | a ssh tab you can open context menu, from context menu there are
        code.mx-1 close other tabs
        |,
        code.mx-1 close tabs on the right
        | , and more function
      li.pb-1 by default,
        code.mx-1 Ctrl + 2
        | will bring electerm window to front, hotkey can be set in
        code.mx-1 setting
        | menu
